content: thearyanag: Merged two small but important PRs this month: #299 adding a node version check (+19/-10 lines) and #374 fixing a fake/spam BTC certificate authority (+1/-1 lines). Activity was sporadic, contributing on just 2 days with a total of 3 commits across 8 modified files (+20/-11 lines). Work was evenly distributed across feature development, bug fixes, and other tasks, with half of the changes focused on documentation improvements.
